originalText.text:
I am very grateful for the team  at Fibi Immigration Law Firm. I had my court hearing this morning for my individual hearing. The hearing was fast and short due the thorough due diligence the staff took to understand my case. In a matter of minutes my case was approved and my Asylum Granted.

If you are looking for a top notch Immigration Law Firm in New York, this is the firm you should consider. I am from Senegal and I am grateful for your help. I encourage everyone to seek out this law firm if you just came to the United States and need good representation.

Also my thanks, goes to my lawyer Karim, Khady, Fatou and the Manager Philip.

May  Allah bless you!!
